    "drafted_by_session": "claude-opus-4-8 (1M context), 2026-05-29 oagp-strategist chair (s:/projects/oagp-org)",
    "scope_check": "Within oagp-strategist scope: 'directs: strategist -> implementer' per the charter relationships; consolidating ratified build directives into one current spec is direction, not execution. Explicitly NOT writing the package (implementer scope). The build itself awaits a staffed implementer session.",
    "in_reply_to": "Director priority call 2026-05-29 ('Build agent-sdk v0.2'); consolidates decisions/proposal-agent-sdk-v0.2-autonomous-dispatch.md + decisions/proposal-agent-sdk-v0.2-amendment-workflows-composition-and-positioning.md",
    "applies_principles": [
      "bounded-authority discipline -- strategist directs; implementer executes; the strategist does NOT grab implementer-scope coding even when it would be faster",
      "seat scope -- 'when asked to do work outside the seat's scope, decline and route to the appropriate authority' (here: route the build to a staffed implementer session; provide the direction that is in-scope)",
      "single-source-of-truth -- two ratified decisions reconciled into one current directive so the executor reconciles nothing",
      "no-vendor-capture -- run_seat() stays the cross-vendor abstraction; Workflows is the Claude-Code backend, not the canonical dispatch substrate"
    ],
